";i:558;s:558:"<ul ><li> The Light Warriors of <em><a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/EightBitTheater' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/EightBitTheater'>8-Bit Theater</a></em> spend lots of time trying to kill each other. <a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WordOfGod' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WordOfGod'>Word Of God</a> has said the monsters and obstacles that they face in the world are nothing compared to the monsters and obstacles within the party.
";i:559;s:515:"</li><li> <em><a class='twikilink' href='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDreamlandChronicles' title='http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheDreamlandChronicles'>The Dreamland Chronicles</a></em>: <a class='urllink' href='http://www.thedreamlandchronicles.com/the-dreamland-chronicles/lies/'>The dwarves don't believe that the elves did not attack with the Nightmare Realm.<img src="http://static.mediatropes.info/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;" /></a>
